flowchart TD
    Start([Webhook Diterima POST /api/webhook/biteship])
    Start --> SigCheck{Verifikasi Signature Header?}
    SigCheck -->|Invalid / Missing| Reject403([HTTP 401/403])
    SigCheck -->|Valid| IpCheck{IP Whitelist?}
    IpCheck -->|Not Whitelisted| Reject403
    IpCheck -->|Whitelisted| Parse[Parse Payload: waybill_id, status, courier]

    Parse --> Return200([HTTP 200 OK - Segera])
    Return200 --> Dispatch[Dispatch Job ke Queue]

    Dispatch --> Job[Job: ProcessBiteshipWebhook]
    Job --> FindShipment[Find shipment by waybill_id atau biteship_order_id]

    FindShipment --> Found{Shipment ditemukan?}
    Found -->|Tidak| LogError[Log Error - Shipment Not Found]
    Found -->|Ya| UpdateTracking[Update shipment.tracking_status]

    UpdateTracking --> StatusType{Status Biteship?}

    StatusType -->|confirmed| OnlyTracking[Update tracking_status saja]
    StatusType -->|in_transit| OnlyTracking
    StatusType -->|failed| LogFailed[NotificationLog: failed delivery]
    StatusType -->|picked_up| PickedUp[TransitionOrderStatus → Shipping]
    StatusType -->|delivered| Delivered[TransitionOrderStatus → Delivered]

    OnlyTracking --> TerminalGuard
    LogFailed --> TerminalGuard
    PickedUp --> NotifyPickup["Kirim WhatsApp: Siap Diambil"]
    Delivered --> NotifyDeliver["Kirim WhatsApp: Pesanan Sampai"]

    TerminalGuard{Order status terminal?}
    TerminalGuard -->|Cancel/Completed/RefundDone/Expire| SkipOrder[Skip order transition]
    TerminalGuard -->|Aktif| ProcessTransition[Proses order transition + notification_logs]

    NotifyPickup --> Done([Selesai])
    NotifyDeliver --> Done
    SkipOrder --> Done
    ProcessTransition --> Done


